data.description: Beautiful brick duplex. 1st floor is 3 bd, 1 bath 1204 sf + 700 LL rec room, laundry hookup and storage. 4-car garage + 2 parking pads for guests! 2nd floor is 662 sf 2 bd, kitchen & LR. 1st floor has all new commercial quality flooring! 2020 new GFA; 2018 15-new Euro-Tech thermo paine windows; 2018 upgraded 260 amp breaker electrical; 2018 new roof. No appliances in either unit.
